                    <span>First introduced to me by a friend, The Precious Present is such a wonderful gift to give yourself.  It's short, but don't dismiss it because of that. Read it out loud to yourself, or read it aloud to someone you love, especially if they are hurting.  This book is very healing.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Inspirational!</div>
